{"tid":842219,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來飼養兔仔可令人心境平靜！🌟","createTime":"2018-09-30T06:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T04:00:35.000Z","uid":197098,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2bb02c27c03019eeb0b33113f23d0caa9caef7","tid":842219,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"兔子是其中一種最心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們尤其是咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是兔子的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！:loveliness:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=SSZloJwmmMd1heVPKxflU1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=c3b97864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a> <br />\n<br />\n當兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)時, 這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活，因為兔子Binky是兔子最開心的狀態。以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=SSZloJwmmMd1heVPKxflU1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=9820c4ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">N.B.:</span> 實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=SSZloJwmmMd1heVPKxflU1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=67d7e6d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"82f3bcc1ec5832238b2cbf1b217c7707ef5ad562","tid":842219,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"竹鼠好啲"},{"pid":"8b9029e4511b8fe3df9c6df891689e592e2fb7ec","tid":842219,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor